OL,3,CCockroaches found at KFC where chicken
OL,4,Cwas stored in dirty containers
OL,6,FA cockroach-infested KFC in Bicester
OL,7,Fhas been ordered to pay #30,000.
OL,9,FThe defendant pleaded guilty to four
OL,10,Ffood hygiene offences in December and
OL,11,Fwas sentenced at Oxford Magistrates
OL,12,FCourt on Tuesday (30 January).
OL,14,FDead flies were also found in a walk-
OL,15,Fin fridge, chicken was stored in dirty
OL,16,Fcontainers, and a washbasin had faulty
OL,17,Fdrainage.
