OL,6,FAs well as the #30,000 fine, the judge
OL,7,Fawarded Cherwell District Council
OL,8,Fcosts of #5,395.88 and ordered the
OL,9,Foffender to pay a #2,000 victim
OL,10,Fsurcharge.
OL,12,FCouncillor Phil Chapman, Portfolio
OL,13,FHolder for Healthy and Safe
OL,14,FCommunities, said: "Hygienic places to
OL,15,Feat out are a key part of what makes
OL,16,Four towns attractive and enjoyable, so
OL,17,Fmaking sure that takeaways and
OL,18,Frestaurants are complying with the law
OL,19,Fis one of our crucial roles.
