OL,4,Cwas stored in dirty containers
OL,6,F"We always look to work with
OL,7,Fbusinesses to help them follow best
OL,8,Fpractice, but we will not hesitate to
OL,9,Ftake formal enforcement action when
OL,10,Fnecessary. This was a shocking case,
OL,11,Fwhich the judge agreed put public
OL,12,Fhealth at risk.
OL,14,F"This verdict is a positive result for
OL,15,Fanyone who enjoys eating out in north
OL,16,FOxfordshire and should serve as a
OL,17,Freminder to other food businesses to
OL,18,Fabide by the law."
